  "translations": {
    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "Around 400 m of crag divided into six sections.\n\nThe routes are either trad or climbed on top-rope. Top-ropes are easy to set up, though in places a considerable length of static rope is required.\n\nRoughly halfway along the crag, there is a less steep section with a path leading up.",
        "method": "llm",
        "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
        "sourceIds": [
          "legacy:kajehallar"
        ]
      },
      "sections": {
        "allmant": {
          "title": {
            "text": "General",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:kajehallar"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "Approximately 400 m of crag divided into six sections.\n\nThe routes are either traditionally protected or climbed on top rope. Setting up top ropes is straightforward, though in places a fair amount of static rope is required.\n\nRoughly halfway along the crag is a less steep section with a path leading up.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:kajehallar"
            ]
          }
        },
        "access": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Access",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:kajehallar"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "There are no houses nearby, and the locals we have met seemed friendly towards and accustomed to climbers.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:kajehallar"
            ]
          }
        },
        "hitta-hit": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Getting there",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:kajehallar"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "The crag is within cycling distance of Halmstad (15 km) and can also be reached by public transport. Take the old Gothenburg road to Kvibille. At the inn, turn onto the road towards Slättåkra and Oskarsström. Continue for approximately 400 metres, then turn left onto Lundsgårdsvägen. Level with Ekegränd, turn right into the woods and follow the right-hand side of the valley. After 300 metres you will reach Originalväggen. Alternatively, turn right onto the forest road before Ekegränd and follow it to the large gravel area, where you can park. From there, walk directly left and diagonally uphill through the woods to reach the top of the crags.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:kajehallar"
            ]
          }
        },
        "klippor": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Crags",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:kajehallar"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:kajehallar"
            ]
          }
